# BoskePulseWidget

WidgetKit extension. Reads `ProductionSnapshot` from App Group via `SnapshotStore`.

## Constraints

- Widget must not perform network calls or hold credentials.
- All data comes from the snapshot JSON written by the main app.
- Support small, medium, and large families.
- Timeline refresh policy ~5 minutes; app triggers reload on snapshot update.

## Shared dependency

Import `BoskePulseCore` for `SnapshotStore`, `Models`, and health types only.
Do not pull in app-only presenters or Keychain code.

## Signing

Requires same App Group entitlement as main app: `group.eu.canopystudio.boske.pulse`.
